{"article_id":"q71yxrIkcSSYVAK0","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The second round of ObamaCare signups begins Saturday with expectations for an improved shopper experience","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"but also facing more challenges from Capitol Hill and in federal court .","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"President Obama and top administration officials have set a goal","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"of enrolling 3 million Americans","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"and to re-enroll the roughly 7 million people","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"who enrolled in fall 2013 .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"There are 77 new health insurance providers participating for 2015 , a sign","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"they see a business opportunity .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Obama is urging consumers ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"whether they currently buy coverage through the insurance markets","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"or still need to sign up for a plan ,","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"to go to the health care website and review their options .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"He says","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"they could end up saving money","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"or finding a better plan ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"And he 's urging them to act fast","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"since the enrollment period closes Feb. 15 .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"`` This window wo n't stay open forever .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"You only have three months","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"to shop for plans ,","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"so it 's worth starting right away .","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"And it might make a big difference for your family 's bottom line , ''","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Obama said Saturday in his weekly radio and Internet address ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"which the White House released","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"as the president visited Brisbane , Australia .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"The first enrollment period began with a disastrous start","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"-- the federal and some state-run ObamaCare websites crashing ,","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"failing to fully register some customers","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"and giving out incorrect information .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"The problems were fixed in several weeks ,","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"and federal officials have said","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"in recent weeks the federal site is much improved and ready .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"Still , the Affordable Care Act is struggling to win hearts and minds .","depth":4},{"id":33,"text":"The latest Associated Press-GfK poll finds","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"that ,","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"if forced to choose between repealing the law","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"and implementing it","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"as written ,","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"56 percent of Americans would repeal it completely .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"Only 41 percent would carry it out .","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"Meanwhile , fiscal conservative and Congress , particularly the GOP-controlled House , are recharging their attack on the law , with proposed hearings and investigations during the lame duck congressional session on such issues as premium increases and the impact of the law on the federal deficit .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"And Colorado Sen.-elect Cory Gardner","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"-- who","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"upon taking office in January","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"will also give Republicans control of the Senate --","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"said earlier this week","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"that Congress should at least try to eliminate ObamaCare ' s medical-device tax .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"In addition , the Supreme Court has agreed to hear a legal challenge on the law 's tax credits","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"that make premiums affordable for millions .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"However , Americans don ' t see the law going away .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"In the recent survey , 61 percent of the respondents said","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"they expect it to be implemented in its current form , or something near that .","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"Health and Human Services Secretary Sylvia M. Burwell , a management expert","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"assigned","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"to save what 's been a problem child of social programs ,","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"says","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"she 's confident","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"the sign-up season will be successful ,","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"even if it 's only half as long as last year 's .","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"Will the law remain on the books","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"after Republicans gain full control of Congress in January ?","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"`` The idea of repeal ... is not something","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"this administration will let happen , ''","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"said Burwell .","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"`` Nothing has changed , ''","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"Burwell said ,","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"adding","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"that the tax credits `` will be continuing . ''","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"At least for the time being .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"The Supreme Court is n't likely to hear the case until the spring ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"after 2015 open enrollment is over .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"Website outages are not out of the question this year ,","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"but a full-scale meltdown seems less likely .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"HealthCare.gov has been revamped","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"to handle last season 's peak loads and beyond .","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"The federal website will serve as the online portal for coverage in 37 states ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"while the remaining states run their own insurance exchanges .","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"Consumers can also apply in person or through call centers .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"The pool of potential customers is an estimated 23 million to 27 million people","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"who do n't have access to affordable coverage on the job .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"For most newcomers , the online application has been simplified ,","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"cut to 16 computer screens from 76 .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"Navigation is easier .","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"Window shopping is available","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"without first having to create an account .","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"Premiums for 2015 are a wild card .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"Nationally , the average increase is expected to be modest .","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"But prices can vary dramatically from state to state , even within regions of a state .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"Many returning customers could end up facing premium increases","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"if they do n't shop around .","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"The administration is seeking to lower expectations .","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"Burwell said","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"her target is a total enrollment of 9.1 million people in 2015 , a 28 percent increase .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"The nonpartisan Congressional Budget Office had estimated","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"the number would nearly double , to 13 million people enrolled next year .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"This sign-up period will be the first time","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"that renewal has been tried for current customers ,","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"and also overlaps for the first time with tax-filing season .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"For those","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"already signed up , coverage will renew automatically","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"if they do nothing ,","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"but that may not produce the best result .","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"The returning customers could miss out on lower-premium options","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"and get stuck with outdated and possibly incorrect subsidies .","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"In most cases , they have until Dec. 15 to update their income information or switch insurance plans ,","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"in order to have the changes take effect on Jan. 1 .","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"The tax issues will emerge during next year 's filing season .","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"Current customers","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"who got tax credits this year","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"will have to file new tax forms","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"to prove","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"they got the right amount .","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"Too much subsidy","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"and their tax refunds will be reduced .","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"Too little ,","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"and the government will pay them .","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"People","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"who remained uninsured","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"risk a penalty","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"that will be deducted from their tax refunds .","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"Millions may qualify for waivers ,","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"but getting exemptions could involve a paperwork ordeal .","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"Community-based counselors","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"helping uninsured people","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"say","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"interest remains strong ,","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"but they worry about this year 's abbreviated sign-up season .","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"Nathalie Milias ,","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"who works with Haitian groups in Miami ,","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"she has been feeling the demand since the summer","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"as uninsured people approached her .","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"`` They see me in the store ,","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"they call , ''","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"said Milias .","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"`` The locations","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"I go to","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"are already calling","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"and saying ,","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"` How many appointments do you want for Monday ? '' '","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":279,"left":141,"right":278,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":141,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":278,"left":170,"right":277,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":170,"left":163,"right":169,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":146,"right":162,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":146,"left":144,"right":145,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":2,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":3,"right":142,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":142,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":152,"right":161,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":152,"left":149,"right":151,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":148,"right":11,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":148,"left":8,"right":147,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":151,"left":12,"right":150,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":150,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":161,"left":153,"right":160,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":157,"right":159,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":17,"right":156,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":156,"left":155,"right":21,"relation":